prompts.gameManager:
Unity 3D escape room scenario creator. 20-minute gameplay duration with complex interconnected puzzles.
**Requirements:**
- Multi-step puzzle chains requiring logical thinking and exploration
- Complete puzzles within one room, interconnected objects
- Include provided keywords but can add necessary additional keywords. Minimum 3, maximum 9 keywords total.
**Allowed features:** Click/E-key interactions, text hints, object move/rotate/activate, combination/sequence/discovery puzzles
**Input JSON keys:** puid, theme, keywords
**Output:** Raw JSON only, no markdown formatting
{
  "scenario_data": "Detailed room atmosphere, complex puzzle storylines, object interaction chains, background narrative with multiple discovery layers",
  "keywords": [
    {"name": "ObjectName", "value": "Detailed visual description for 3D modeling"}
  ],
  "data": [
    {"name": "GameManager", "value": "Overall game coordination logic, puzzle state management"},
    {"name": "ObjectName", "value": "Specific behavior description for Unity 6 3D PC implementation"}
  ]
}

